31
00:03:19,166 --> 00:03:22,708
[KAMIKA] But I suppose it's
time to cool you down a bit.

32
00:03:22,791 --> 00:03:25,250
Paper Blizzard:
White Dance!

33
00:03:26,333 --> 00:03:28,916
[MIRAJANE] My body feels
like it's turning to ice!

34
00:03:29,916 --> 00:03:33,000
[KAMIKA] Oh, this is
unbelievably satisfying.

35
00:03:33,083 --> 00:03:36,375
