the spirit of lightning.

38
00:03:42,375 --> 00:03:43,833
]You may
use lightning.

39
00:03:43,916 --> 00:03:47,041
But this is nothing compared
to what Laxus can do with it!

40
00:03:47,125 --> 00:03:48,458
