like more pain?

41
00:03:48,541 --> 00:03:49,708
Then perhaps I can
give you a taste

42
00:03:49,791 --> 00:03:52,625
of what true agony feels like.

43
00:03:55,916 --> 00:04:01,458
[KAMIKA] Paper Blizzard:
Green Dance.

44
00:04:01,541 --> 00:04:03,750
[MIRAJANE] What is this?!

45
00:04:03,833 --> 00:04:06,250
