238
00:11:41,416 --> 00:11:43,250
[WENDY grunting]

239
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,083
[LEADER] You're only
postponing the inevitable.

240
00:11:49,166 --> 00:11:50,541
Your fire magic is useless,

241
00:11:50,625 --> 00:11:52,666
and your attacks have not
